{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.94,"min_p":0.85,"low_token_fraction":0.05,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000008","id":"schlegel-4-2-u1","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"So viele Gäste lad’, als hier geschrieben!","ts":"2026-01-23T19:01:10Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.94,"min_p":0.85,"low_token_fraction":0.05,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000001","id":"schlegel-4-2-d2","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"[Regie] (Ein Bedienter ab.)","ts":"2026-01-23T19:01:20Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.94,"min_p":0.85,"low_token_fraction":0.05,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000001","id":"schlegel-4-2-u3","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"[Bedienter] Ihr sollt gewiß keine schlechten kriegen, gnäd’ger Herr; denn ich will erst zusehn, ob sie sich die Finger ablecken können.","ts":"2026-01-23T19:01:30Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.72,"min_p":0.42,"low_token_fraction":0.25,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000008","id":"schlegel-4-2-u4","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"Was soll das für eine Probe sein?","ts":"2026-01-23T19:01:40Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.94,"min_p":0.85,"low_token_fraction":0.05,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000001","id":"schlegel-4-2-u5","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"[Zweiter Bedienter] Ei, gnädiger Herr, das wäre ein schlechter Koch, der seine eignen Finger nicht ablecken könnte. Darum, wer das nicht kann, der geht nicht mit mir.","ts":"2026-01-23T19:01:50Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.81,"min_p":0.51,"low_token_fraction":0.15,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000008","id":"schlegel-4-2-u6","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"Geh, mach fort. –","ts":"2026-01-23T19:02:00Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.94,"min_p":0.85,"low_token_fraction":0.05,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000001","id":"schlegel-4-2-d7","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"[Regie] (Bedienter ab.)","ts":"2026-01-23T19:02:10Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.94,"min_p":0.85,"low_token_fraction":0.05,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000004","id":"schlegel-4-2-u8","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"Ja, wahrhaftig.","ts":"2026-01-23T19:02:20Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.61,"min_p":0.28,"low_token_fraction":0.35,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000008","id":"schlegel-4-2-u9","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"Wohl! Gutes stiftet er vielleicht bei ihr; Sie ist ein albern, eigensinnig Ding.","ts":"2026-01-23T19:02:30Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.94,"min_p":0.85,"low_token_fraction":0.05,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000001","id":"schlegel-4-2-d10","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"[Regie] (Julia tritt auf.)","ts":"2026-01-23T19:02:40Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.94,"min_p":0.85,"low_token_fraction":0.05,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000004","id":"schlegel-4-2-u11","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"Seht, wie sie fröhlich aus der Beichte kommt.","ts":"2026-01-23T19:02:50Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.83,"min_p":0.31,"low_token_fraction":0.07,"token_count":30},"discord_id":"100000000000000008","id":"schlegel-4-2-u12","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"Nun, Starrkopf? Sag, wo bist herumgeschwärmt?","ts":"2026-01-23T19:03:00Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.81,"min_p":0.51,"low_token_fraction":0.15,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000003","id":"schlegel-4-2-u13","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"Wo ich gelernt, die Sünde zu bereun Hartnäck’gen Ungehorsams gegen euch Und eu’r Gebot, und wo der heil’ge Mann Mir auferlegt, vor euch mich hinzuwerfen, Vergebung zu erflehn. – Vergebt, ich bitt’ euch; Von nun an will ich stets euch folgsam sein.","ts":"2026-01-23T19:03:10Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.72,"min_p":0.42,"low_token_fraction":0.25,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000008","id":"schlegel-4-2-u14","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"Schickt nach dem Grafen, geht und sagt ihm dies. Gleich morgen früh will ich dies Band geknüpft sehn.","ts":"2026-01-23T19:03:20Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.94,"min_p":0.85,"low_token_fraction":0.05,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000003","id":"schlegel-4-2-u15","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"Ich traf den jungen Grafen bei Lorenzo, Und alle Huld und Lieb’ erwies ich ihm, So das Gesetz der Zucht nicht übertritt.","ts":"2026-01-23T19:03:30Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.94,"min_p":0.85,"low_token_fraction":0.05,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000008","id":"schlegel-4-2-u16","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"Nun wohl, das freut mich, das ist gut! – Steh auf! So ist es recht. – Laßt mich den Grafen sehn. Potztausend! Geht, sag ich, und holt ihn her. – So wahr Gott lebt, der würd’ge fromme Pater, Von unsrer ganzen Stadt verdient er Dank.","ts":"2026-01-23T19:03:40Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.94,"min_p":0.85,"low_token_fraction":0.05,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000003","id":"schlegel-4-2-u17","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"Kommt, Amme! Wollt ihr mit mir auf mein Zimmer? Mir helfen Putz erlesen, wie ihr glaubt, Daß mir geziemt, ihn morgen anzulegen?","ts":"2026-01-23T19:03:50Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.94,"min_p":0.85,"low_token_fraction":0.05,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000009","id":"schlegel-4-2-u18","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"Nein, nicht vor Donnerstag; es hat noch Zeit.","ts":"2026-01-23T19:04:00Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.61,"min_p":0.28,"low_token_fraction":0.35,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000008","id":"schlegel-4-2-u19","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"Geh mit ihr, Amme! Morgen geht’s zur Kirche.","ts":"2026-01-23T19:04:10Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.81,"min_p":0.51,"low_token_fraction":0.15,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000001","id":"schlegel-4-2-d20","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"[Regie] (Julia und die Amme ab.)","ts":"2026-01-23T19:04:20Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.94,"min_p":0.85,"low_token_fraction":0.05,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000009","id":"schlegel-4-2-u21","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"Die Zeit wird kurz zu unsrer Anstalt fallen; Es ist fast Nacht.","ts":"2026-01-23T19:04:30Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.94,"min_p":0.85,"low_token_fraction":0.05,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000008","id":"schlegel-4-2-u22","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"Blitz! Ich will frisch mich rühren, Und alles soll schon gehn, Frau, dafür steh’ ich. Geh du zu Julien, hilf an ihrem Putz. Ich gehe nicht zu Bett: laß mich gewähren. Ich will die Hausfrau diesmal machen. – Heda! – Kein Mensch zur Hand? – Gut, ich will selber gehn Zum Grafen Paris, um ihn anzutreiben Auf morgen früh: mein Herz ist mächtig leicht, Seit dies verkehrte Mädchen sich besonnen.","ts":"2026-01-23T19:04:40Z"}
{"confidence":{"mean_p":0.94,"min_p":0.85,"low_token_fraction":0.05,"token_count":12},"discord_id":"100000000000000001","id":"schlegel-4-2-d23","kind":"UtteranceAppended","session_id":"schlegel-4-2","status":"final","text":"[Regie] (Capulet und die Gräfin ab.)","ts":"2026-01-23T19:04:50Z"}
